Package common.hardware.limelight

Class Limelight

java.lang.Object
common.hardware.limelight.Limelight
public class Limelight extends Object
Software wrapper to obtain data from and send data to the physical Limelight. LIMELIGHT CONVENTIONS: - When the target is right of the vertical centerline, tx is positive. - When the target is above the horizontal centerline, ty is positive.

  • Constructor Details

    • Limelight

      public Limelight(String hostname, double cameraAngle, double cameraHeight, double frontDistance, double robotCenterDistance)
      Parameters:
      cameraAngle - - The vertical angle of the limelight. Leaning backwards is positive degrees.
      cameraHeight - - The height off of the ground of the limelight lens
      frontDistance - - The distance between the front of the robot and the Limelight Lens
      robotCenterDistance - - The distance between the center of the robot and the Limelight Lens
